labels.name: E:Desktop Discord Import And Archive Protocol

body:
# Bug Report

## Description

Status Desktop crashed when I entered the password.
Was fine when I opened it again

## Steps to reproduce

1. Launch on command line
2. enter password
3. weep

#### Expected behavior

Men don't cry.

#### Actual behavior

Yes cry.

### Additional Information

- Status desktop version: v0.12.0-85bbd3-x86_64
- Operating System: Linux Fedora
